    "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nif you see the need to report hashrate to geth, you can do it using the `ethash_submitHashrate` RPC API method.\r\n\r\nSource:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/d8ff53dfb8a516f47db37dbc7fd7ad18a1e8a125/consensus/ethash/api.go#L92\r\n\r\nExample:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\", \"id\": 1, \"method\": \"ethash_submitHashrate\", \"params\": [\"0xf3f3f3\", \"0x50d858e0985ecc7f60418aaf0cc5ab587f42c2570a884095a9e8ccacd0f6545c\"]}\r\n```",
